= Updating items in Array State

Objective: Every time whne the user clicks "Generate emojis", emojis icons should be updated.

App.js

1 ) Update emoji value in the emojis array for passes emoji id

— Use the setEmojis function to change the value of an emoji in the emojis array based on the given emoji id . Pass the previous state to the setEmojis function. Return a new emojis array where the emoji with the matching id gets updated to newEmoji.
— To create the new array, use the map method on the emojis array.
— To decide if you should return the new emoji or keep the old one, you can use: if/else statement or conditional (ternary) operator.